ry, till the 21st century, handbags have doubled up as both a statement piece and practical element in the lives of everyday women.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So, whats the best way to choose the right bag for you? Do you opt for the trendy route, or something more classic? Well, whatever your choice may be, here is our guide to understanding some of the biggest bag trends this fashion:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Choose a bag that matches your personality</strong>:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Are you an introvert, or an extrovert? Do you like bright colours or neutrals? Well, the good news is, regardless of your personality type, theres a bag out there: crafted and coloured that will tickle your fancy through any fashion season!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Classic shapes</em>&nbsp;like the<strong>&nbsp;tote or sling</strong>, in&nbsp;<strong>neutral tones,</strong>&nbsp;<strong>would suit you if youre a person who doesnt like to experiment a lot with colour or shape</strong>. The best part about having a classic handbag, is that even through its simple structure, it will be able to add spice to any outfit no matter the occasion. Itll give you classic vibes through any fashion cycle.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If youre someone who likes to experiment with your look and likes to make a statement with their look.&nbsp;<em>Unconventional shapes</em>, like the&nbsp;<strong>box-sling, or over-sized bags in bright, bold colours will be the way to go!&nbsp;</strong>These type of bags add drama and super-size any normal, everyday outfit. Not to mention, will bring all the eyes in the room onto you and your eloquently styled bag!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Want to find the bag thats right for you? Browse our catalogue for more options!</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Textures, Textures, Textures</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Suede, leather, or quilted. With so many options, how do you know which texture is right for you? Well, ask the weather! Most fashionistas say, that the weather is a great way to determine which fabric you should go for. Leather is usually a fabric that is versatile and works through all the seasons.&nbsp;<strong>And with vegan leather packing a punch this fashion season, why not?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Leather bags also have a classy appeal to them, making them a versatile choice to make this fashion season! So adopt your perfect vegan leather bag this fashion season, youll be trendy no matter the weather outside.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ethical fashion is a major concern this fashion cycle. With a rise in the need for finding ethical ways to reproduce trendy pieces, vegan fashion has found a sweet spot in the fashion trend market. Now more than ever, there is a gravitation towards&nbsp;cruelty-free bags, that also stay trendy no matter what. Its out with the non-ethical bags and in, with the versatile,&nbsp;vegan bags this fashion season!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Broke Mate, is a company that supports the ethical treatment of animals. All our bags, are 100% vegan and crafted with pure-cruelty free love! Explore our universe of ethical fashion, shop now.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '584-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-10-18 02:40:37', '2022-10-18 02:40:37', '', 584, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=622', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
